rd，我都唔會走去熄咗佢，係次次等佢彈出嚟等到火滾，快則一兩秒(要一兩秒先彈個視窗出嚟問一個password，都唔知佢點implement，完全接受唔到)，慢則30秒至一分鐘，尤其硬件交差嘅機。至少問下password依啲，係linux上唔會慢到咁。"},{"pid":"4aace3dabdcf280e1875f9926a84e3c7c6a6c677","tid":205623,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當on9 users 全部轉去 Linux Linux 都會好on9<br />\n個個人 chmod 777，download 病毒之後照打admin password <br />\n幾聰明嘅系統都敵不過 on9 users</blockquote><br />\n無端端 chmod 777 做乜 ?</blockquote><br />\n正如d人熄左UAC一樣</blockquote><br />\nUAC係拖慢部機，佢如果好地地問下password，我都唔會走去熄咗佢，係次次等佢彈出嚟等到火滾，快則一兩秒(要一兩秒先彈個視窗出嚟問一個password，都唔知佢點implement，完全接受唔到)，慢則30秒至一分鐘，尤其硬件交差嘅機。至少問下password依啲，係linux上唔會慢到咁。</blockquote><br />\n我最多都只係熄轉暗screen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0313ad6e20857271bbe6dc6c5d1dd34f74284f6a","tid":205623,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當on9 users 全部轉去 Linux Linux 都會好on9<br />\n個個人 chmod 777，download 病毒之後照打admin password <br />\n幾聰明嘅系統都敵不過 on9 users</blockquote><br />\n無端端 chmod 777 做乜 ?</blockquote><br />\n正如d人熄左UAC一樣</blockquote><br />\nUAC係拖慢部機，佢如果好地地問下password，我都唔會走去熄咗佢，係次次等佢彈出嚟等到火滾，快則一兩秒(要一兩秒先彈個視窗出嚟問一個password，都唔知佢點implement，完全接受唔到)，慢則30秒至一分鐘，尤其硬件交差嘅機。至少問下password依啲，係linux上唔會慢到咁。</blockquote><br />\n我最多都只係熄轉暗screen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUAC真係慢撚到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}